tags: lauki ka cheela recipe in hindi
description:
Dosto, lockdown chal raha hain, mummy aaj Lauki ke Cheele ki recipe share kar rahi hain.. Jarur se try kijiega, sab khushi se enjoy karenge! 

CookingShooking ko jarur subscribe karein -  https://goo.gl/MH3A4r

Instagram me follow jarur karein - https://www.instagram.com/cooking.shooking

English videos - https://goo.gl/Sxk4Fp

Ingredients Lauki ke Cheele ke lie
Lauki / Bottle Gourd - 1 medium
Adrak - 1 inch
Hari Mirch - 2
Fresh Dhaniya - thora sa
Besan - 200g / 1 1/2 cup
Namak - 1 1/2 tsp / taste hisab se
Lal Mirch Powder - 1 tsp
Jeera - 1 tsp
Pani - batter banane ke lie
Oil - cheela sekne ke lie

Kitchen Products I use:
Measuring Cup & Spoon Set - https://amzn.to/2KZBVpq
Kitchen Weight Scale - https://amzn.to/2ug3G65 
Instant Yeast - https://amzn.to/2N2wzuf (500gms, keep frozen in airtight container, will stay good for years)
Instant Yeast - https://amzn.to/2KZSkdn (small pack)
